# Config contracts

- **YAML only** on disk; serialize with `io.atomic_yaml_dump`, load with `io.load_yaml`.
- Validate all configs with `src.utils.validators` (job, machine, luts, stroke).
- Do not duplicate constants: bounds/units come from schema YAML and `validators`.
- When adding fields, update schema + validator + tests (`tests/test_schemas.py`).